{"tid":1102434,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"PC版《人中之龍極2》5月發售，Steam商店開放預購中","createTime":"2019-04-11T16:29:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T06:21:18.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"39a051d7980a402496ff2ec90d3aebd1db302ed4","tid":1102434,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T16:29:11.000Z","msg":"2017 年 PS4 平台重製登場的 SEGA 系列名作《人中之龍極 2》（Yakuza Kiwami 2），發行商 SEGA 確認 5 月登上 PC Steam 平台，目前商店頁面開放預購中。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.4gamers.com.tw/ckfinder/images/Why%20Lee/News/2019.04/ss_c90b9d21ee15ffaec35395e9f2bf72ffb135fbb0.1920x1080.jpg?versionId=LmakXkEHi0IFU0DD5mdb67L5xH0qUupU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.4gamers.com.tw%2Fckfinder%2Fimages%2FWhy%2520Lee%2FNews%2F2019.04%2Fss_c90b9d21ee15ffaec35395e9f2bf72ffb135fbb0.1920x1080.jpg%3FversionId%3DLmakXkEHi0IFU0DD5mdb67L5xH0qUupU&h=b50b3a1e&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n重製後的《人中之龍極 2》有著令人驚豔的 4K 畫質和解鎖幀率限制<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。2 代的故事中，「堂島之龍」桐生一馬必須面對野心勃勃的「關西之龍」鄉田龍司，一馬必須前往大阪蒼天堀，與敵對幫派之間進行和平協商。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.4gamers.com.tw/ckfinder/images/Why%20Lee/News/2019.04/ss_b93a204285a873090fb9dd12eb4ac34f6f001984.1920x1080.jpg?versionId=OPd7UlqV5oG9QFAJMpxCD_RclMCb7AMv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.4gamers.com.tw%2Fckfinder%2Fimages%2FWhy%2520Lee%2FNews%2F2019.04%2Fss_b93a204285a873090fb9dd12eb4ac34f6f001984.1920x1080.jpg%3FversionId%3DOPd7UlqV5oG9QFAJMpxCD_RclMCb7AMv&h=f2c076f3&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n盡情遊玩粉絲們最愛的小遊戲，包括更新過的「風化島公關俱樂部」和「幫派創造者」，或者前往全新打造的遊戲中心，遊玩初代《電腦戰機》大型電玩、高爾夫賓果及《Toylets》等新遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.4gamers.com.tw/ckfinder/images/Why%20Lee/News/2019.04/ss_d830318db32bf095becd8670f0ea698d7d07c102.1920x1080.jpg?versionId=B9I39Amyegeu5MoufpoJjkXeJp68swvO\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.4gamers.com.tw%2Fckfinder%2Fimages%2FWhy%2520Lee%2FNews%2F2019.04%2Fss_d830318db32bf095becd8670f0ea698d7d07c102.1920x1080.jpg%3FversionId%3DB9I39Amyegeu5MoufpoJjkXeJp68swvO&h=155ee73b&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n《人中之龍極 2》（Yakuza Kiwami 2）PC Steam 版預計於 5 月 9 日發售，售價港幣 222 元。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.4gamers.com.tw/ckfinder/images/Why%20Lee/News/2019.04/YK2_PO_DLC_ARRAY_616wide_UK_V4.jpg?versionId=3NAVWhoSuJsXFbdBSUbHxYcZyNcotsnX\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.4gamers.com.tw%2Fckfinder%2Fimages%2FWhy%2520Lee%2FNews%2F2019.04%2FYK2_PO_DLC_ARRAY_616wide_UK_V4.jpg%3FversionId%3D3NAVWhoSuJsXFbdBSUbHxYcZyNcotsnX&h=f7515d33&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/38519/yakuza-kiwami-2-announced-for-pc-release-date-confirmed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.4gamers.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F38519%2Fyakuza-kiwami-2-announced-for-pc-release-date-confirmed&d=Cuyai%2BbkQ%2BZKjwazMoctzj2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=08d86e7f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/38519/yakuza-kiwami-2-announced-for-pc-release-date-confirmed</a>"},{"pid":"de30afc47ecabdba49ffa4c2a2927647106e303e","tid":1102434,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T16:30:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">系統需求</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n最低配備:<br />\n作業系統: Windows 7 (64-Bit Required)<br />\n處理器: Intel Core i5-3470, 3.2 GHz / AMD Ryzen 3 1200, 3.1 GHz<br />\n記憶體: 4 GB 記憶體<br />\n顯示卡: GeForce GTX 660, 2 GB / Radeon HD 7870, 2 GB<br />\nDirectX: 版本：11<br />\n儲存空間: 42 GB 可用空間<br />\n備註: Pre-set Graphics Setting: Low, Target FPS: 30FPS (1080p at 75% render scale)<br />\n<br />\n建議配備:<br />\n作業系統: Windows 10 (64-Bit Required)<br />\n處理器: Intel Core i7-6700, 3.4 GHz / AMD Ryzen 7 1700, 3.7 GHz<br />\n記憶體: 16 GB 記憶體<br />\n顯示卡: GeForce GTX 1070, 8 GB / Radeon RX Vega 56, 8GB<br />\nDirectX: 版本：11<br />\n儲存空間: 42 GB 可用空間<br />\n備註: Pre-set Graphics Setting: High, Target FPS: 60FPS @1080p"},{"pid":"a1c50eabcbfd845317fbe4fbae89feaafc465818","tid":1102434,"uid":201992,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T16:31:54.000Z","msg":"Xboxone Contana 留名系統啟動，<br />\n請勿負評干擾運作。"},{"pid":"c2bb65af327575b2b78762635b364c882fa5ba5e","tid":1102434,"uid":81113,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T17:14:32.000Z","msg":"MHW又有PC<br />\n<br />\n人中又有PC<br />\n<br />\n我部PS4 pro賣得啦"},{"pid":"3b7d67f6d721f5bffb025b9c896be8ace1de0068","tid":1102434,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T17:59:48.000Z","msg":"快手0-6快UP上去"},{"pid":"3bdbb75e25d7a09f6e95eea21d2adca4388f83f2","tid":1102434,"uid":124268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T01:35:24.000Z","msg":"照道理跟推出次序唔係人中6出先，點解會俾極2爬左頭?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3df92152707d8d0d9d1ff90e99e40b5e4da318b3","tid":1102434,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3bdbb75e25d7a09f6e95eea21d2adca4388f83f2","tid":1102434,"uid":124268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T01:35:24.000Z","msg":"照道理跟推出次序唔係人中6出先，點解會俾極2爬左頭?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T03:54:20.000Z","msg":"如果只係玩過PC版01<br />\n你一野跳去6大結局<br />\n重有鬼人玩中間3-5<br />\n集集地圖近乎一樣"},{"pid":"99f229338a733525a081009a05139d2ce2585b05","tid":1102434,"uid":40152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T04:04:03.000Z","msg":"字幕係Sony 擁有，所以今集係咪都一樣冇中文字幕？"},{"pid":"6efd51829081cbb7b260288ed276e1592cf63e8f","tid":1102434,"uid":26200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3df92152707d8d0d9d1ff90e99e40b5e4da318b3","tid":1102434,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"p